The Group Stage of the TotalEnergies Africa Cup of Nations (AFCON), Cameroun 2021 was concluded on Thursday. Sixteen teams continue their road towards the Holy Grail of African football, which will be decided on February 6, 2022. Following are some of the Group Stage Stats: Vincent Aboubakar of CameroOn Matches Played: 36
Goals Scored: 68 (1.89 goals / match) • Top Goal Scorer: Vincent Abubakar (Cameroon) – 5 goals • Team with highest points: Nigeria – nine points • Team with lowest points: Mauritania – 0 points • Team with highest goals scored: Cameroon – seven goals • Team with lowest goals scored: Guinea Bissau, Mauritania – 0 goals • Team with highest goals conceded: Mauritania – seven goals • Team with lowest goals conceded: Senegal – 0 goals